================================
=== OCS List of Attendees Plugin
=== Version: $Id$
=== Author: Péter Fankhauser <pfankhauser@ethz.ch>
================================

About
-----
This plugin allows to show a list of attendees of a conference.

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file COPYING for the complete terms of this license.

System Requirements
-------------------
Same requirements as the OCS 2.3 core.

Configuration
------------
Add the attendees list page in the navigation bar by adding a new navbar item in "Website Management > Website Headers, Footers, Lists and Navigation Bar > 3.4 Navigation Bar" with label name "plugins.generic.listOfAttendees.navigationTitle" and URL "/ocs/index.php/dw2014/dw2014/attendees" (adapt the URL to your installation setup).